snippet.title: Toy Unboxing: Max and Ruby open a Twisti Scooter!
snippet.description:
We challenged our Razor Jr. kids to unbox the super cute Twisti scooter. Our cameras captured the silly antics of Max and Ruby as they try to free the toy from its package.Usually a task left to mom or dad, the kids finally succeed and go out for a ride! Check out this adorably cute clip from Razor Jr.!

Also check out how to make Olaf, from Frozen out of a Twisti scooter: http://youtu.be/gBGwRsL2Suo

…And then see the Olaf Twisti scooter in action with Anna (sung by Ruby) performing Do You Want To Build a Snowman: http://youtu.be/I33R72GGgc4

The Twisti toddler ride-on is the cutest bug that invites little movers to take a fun ride. With darling Little Buzz and Lady Buzz bumble bee designs, kids simply have a seat, rest their feet, and they're off – moving the handlebars side-to-side to propel themselves. Twisti's bright eyes follow along, moving back-and-forth for a real bug's eye view! This scooter is designed for 18 months and up (up to 55 pounds.) 

Always wear appropriate safety equipment.  Exercise caution and common sense – do not assume you can easily to everything you may see on a video, because all trick or aggressive riding takes practice and involves increased risks.  Always check local laws regarding use of electric-powered products.

Learn more at: http://www.razor.com/razor-jr/products/razor-jr/twisti/
The Twisti is available at Target in-stores and online: 
http://www.target.com/p/razor-razor-jr-twisti-lady-buzz/-/A-15311999#prodSlot=medium_1_2&term=twisti

snippet.title: Thomas & Friends™ Talking Thomas and Percy Set
snippet.description:
This is a paid advertisement for Fisher-Price. #ad

Hi guys! We've got the brand new Thomas & Friends™ Talking Thomas & Percy Train Set today on Kids Toys Play! This is our new favourite toy train set, and we're having so much fun watching these two best friends interact with each other! Whether they're racing the rails, causing confusion and delay, or being really useful, Thomas and Percy can't stop talking to each other! Watch us build multiple track layouts, tell a story, and have fun together, and the BEST Thomas Trackmaster set we've ever had! Available at Walmart!


Sodor is usually an island in the middle of the ocean, but sometimes, with the Fisher-Price® Thomas & Friends™ Talking Thomas & Percy Train Set, Sodor can also be in the living room. This highly detailed playset features favorite places from the island of Sodor, including the Vicarstown Bridge, the Railyard, the Brendam docks, and Blue Mountain. It also includes motorized Thomas and Percy train engines who recognize and talk to each other when they meet on the track! Young conductors can help Thomas and Percy work together by dropping boulders down in the Blue Mountain cave for them to load and unload along with other cargo at Bulstrode the boat and by creating their own exciting adventures all around Sodor.

Thomas & Friends™ motorized train set featuring TrackMaster™ track and several classic Island of Sodor locations from content
Motorized Thomas and Percy engines stop to talk with each other when they meet on the track, and both have cargo cars for loading and unloading around the island
Kid-controlled track switches and a control panel allow little engineers to stop engines for side-by-side interactions and control which way they go
Combine this track with any other Thomas & Friends™ train set to create even bigger Sodor adventures! (Track sets sold separately and subject to availability.)
Great gift for preschool children 3 years and older

snippet.title: Unboxing of Giant frozen tent toy (Anna and Elsa) for kids up to 3years
snippet.description:
Gia, a 3-year-old girl, took the time to unpack her new Frozen inspired play tent.
This girl is suitable for children aged 3 and over because these dimensions allow them to easily reach even their parents!
Our little Gia and her mother, she especially likes that the tent is big and highlights the main characters of the cartoons "Frozen" namely Elsa and Anna on one side and on the other side we see Christoph and Donkey . This tent toy is perfect for small children who admire "governing" a space dedicated to them as a Playhouse to discover new things they previously did not know either alone or even with their parents! indeed, and with this tent, they will be able to develop as many skills and qualities that will be useful to them once grown.
In addition, this tent can be a real storage tool for your children's favorite toys as you will gain storage space and your children will no longer lose their favorite toys!
Designed with as much finesse and ingenuity, this tent is easy to fold / unfold even for your little ones and light enough to carry with you when you plan to travel
Dimensions of the frozen tent (Anna and Elsa): 1m6cm / 1m6cm / 1m29cm

Surprise and Play is a family-friendly YouTube channel for kids and toy enthusiasts. We unbox toys, open egg surprises and have lots of fun! snippet.title: Five Nights At Freddy's Toys for Kids FNAF Toys Unboxing Set Puppet  Toy Review Bonnie Chica funko
snippet.description:
Five Nights At Freddy's Toys for Kids FNAF Toys Unboxing Set Puppet  Toy Review Bonnie Chica funko Toys. These toys are like the funco toys. Jazzy Puppet's FNAF Toys come to life and do Jumpscares in this Five Nights at Freddy's 5 Inch action figure toy review. Five Nights at Freddy's Toys for kids are super fun!  You will love this FNAF 5 Inch Articulated Funko toy unboxing with FNAF stop motion! The Five Nights at Freddy's toys are supposed to stay on the shelf, but they come to live, eat all of the dogs food, and then run away! Jazzy Puppet screams when the Five Nights at Freddy's Jumpscares happen! They are funny FNAF jumpscares though! Non of the FNAF Jump Scares are not scary. You will laugh at this funny Five Night's at Freddys Halloween Video for kids! Jazzy meets some really fun FNAF Toys! She Meets Freddy Fazbear, Toy Chika, Toy Bonnie, and Foxy! They come to live and are so funny! This is a FNAF not scary video for children to enjoy. The four Five Nights at Freddy's action figures are so cool! My favorite is the Toy Chica FNAF action figure, and I love FNAF videos! These are similar to FNAF Mcfarlane toys and come from the FNAF world! You will love this family friendly video. It is a super fun family friendly toy review for kids that is perfect for Halloween! Thank you for visiting the Jazzy Puppet Show! 
Here are the toys that she is Unboxing and doing a Toy Review on: 
Freddy Fazbear, Toy Bonnie, Toy Chica, Toy Chika, and Toy Foxy. This set is like the FNAF Funko toys! The FNAF toy set also came with a Golden Freddy Fazbear, but the Freddy bear didn't make it into the FNAF kid's video! Maybe next time Golden Freddy will come and play. We'll have to get him from FNAF world! =)

snippet.title: Birthday Haul! Nerf Elite and X-Shot Blaster Unboxing and Review
snippet.description:
We're celebrating a birthday on Kids Toys Play, by unboxing some awesome Nerf review and Zuru X-Shot blasters! We've got the Nerf N-Strike Elite Roughcut 2x4 and Zuru X-Shot Flying Bug Attack and 2x Xcess sets, and a ton of darts! We even have the new Thomas and Friends trackmaster push along Birthday Celebration train set! Lots to unbox and review on our family friendly channel for kids!

Zuru X-Shot Flying Bug Attack Double Swarm Seeker 0:15
Take down flying targets with X-Shot Flying Bug Attack! Place your bugs onto the motorized launcher, step on the pedal and release it to see bugs soar in the air. Take them down with the exclusive Swarm-Seeker blaster!

KEY FEATURES:

• Real Flying Bug Attack that hover in the air for you to blast down!

• Motorized launcher that works by pressing its button down with your foot so you have your hands free to shot down the bugs!

• Release the pedal and watch your bugs fly through the air. Take them down before they land!

• The Swarm-Seeker is specially tailored for quick fire with its 10 dart capacity magazine so you\'ll have plenty of shots to hit your targets!

Zuru X-Shot 2x Xcess 1:07
With a pull to prime mechanism and a dual dart system firing both discs and darts, from a special rotating double barrel system, your opponent won’t know what hit them!

KEY FEATURES:

• Shoots darts up to 80ft/24m

• 6 Dart Capacity (each) Dual Barrel

• Discs for short range targets

PACK INCLUDES:

1x X-Shot XCESS Blaster

12x X-Shot Foam Darts

Nerf N-Strike Elite Roughcut 2x4 2:00
Slam into battle with the double-barreled excellence of the ROUGH CUT 2X4 blaster! This sleek blaster lets you launch 2 Elite Darts at once at targets up to 75 feet away, and the pump-action design lets you pump repeatedly to unleash a steady double stream of darts! Launch up to 8 Elite Darts without reloading! As with most N-STRIKE blasters, the Tactical Rail lets you add most N-STRIKE Tactical Rail accessories (sold separately) for more battle capability. Power up the multishot madness of the ROUGH CUT 2X4 blaster and get ready to dominate with both barrels!

 Thanks for watching, thumbs up if you enjoyed our video!

snippet.title: FurReal Friends - 'Roarin' Tyler, The Playful Tiger - UNBOXING - Kids love the wild soft toy 🐯
snippet.description:
See the happiest girl in the world when Aria finds 'Roarin' Tyler, The wild Playful Tiger is waiting for her after school. Aria unboxes, her new tiger friend, and plays with him. Pippy, her dog, plays too! 
Tyler has over 100 sound and motion combinations so he’s pretty much as interactive as they come. When your kiddos make sounds or roar at him, he’ll bow and playfully roar right back at them! His back legs move as does his head and ears to it’s really like he’s about to come alive. Luckily he’s just a soft fur toy with deep green eyes so everyone at home is safe!

Tyler is also interactive in other ways outside of his cute little roar. If you pet his forehead, his back, or his muzzle he’s respond with a variety of movements and tiger-like sounds. But don’t worry, he’s also soft enough to hug and cuddle all day long too. One of our other favorite things is the little toy rubber chicken that comes with Tyler. That’s his play toy to and he loves to play and interact with him too. And when that chicken squeaks, Tyler the Tiger is all into it.

snippet.title: Fishing Time!  Backyard Bass Toy Unboxing, Review, and Play by a kid (and Dad too)
snippet.description:
Get your own Backyard Bass Casting Game for Kids on Amazon.com here: http://www.amazon.com/dp/B0007IQAIG/?tag=connorscorner-20

Connor and his dad join up in this video for the first time.  They play the game first over concrete.  Then they try and get adventurous and go into the water... but the fish gets blown to the other side of the lake!   

Backyard Bass is a fishing game that helps kids learn and practice how to cast.  It uses a weighted plug, so there are no dangerous, sharp fishing hooks while learning.  It can be used on a flat surface or in the water like a pool or lake (but don't let your fish get blown away!) 

There are different sized sets from 3 to 16 for larger groups or just more fish to catch if you are casting over a large area. This toy game is especially for those aged 6 and up.
